2379	[Determinant of the identity with one column replaced]
2380	  \label{lem:gr_det_one_updateCol}
2381	  \lean{AlgebraicGeometry.Grassmannian.det_one_updateCol}
2382	  For a vector \(v : \mathrm{Fin}\,d \to R\) and a row index \(p\), the determinant of the identity
2383	  matrix with its \(p\)-th column replaced by \(v\) is the entry \(v_p\), with \emph{no} sign:
2384	  \(\det\bigl((1).\mathrm{updateCol}\,p\,v\bigr) = v_p\).
2385	\end{lemma}
2386	\begin{proof}
