2388	\leanok
2389	  By Cramer's rule \(\det((1).\mathrm{updateCol}\,p\,v) = ((1).\mathrm{cramer}\,v)_p\)
2390	  (\(\mathrm{Matrix.cramer\_apply}\)); and \((1).\mathrm{cramer}\,v = v\) since
2391	  \(\mathrm{1}\cdot\mathrm{cramer}\,v = \det(1)\cdot v = v\) (\(\mathrm{Matrix.mulVec\_cramer}\)).
2392	  Proved directly in Lean.
